Subject: [PATCH] prompt v1: "Within the carousel, exchange the positions of the 'musical notes' image and the 'sunrise' image."
---
Index: onboardingandauthentication/src/main/java/com/ibm/google/onboardingandauthentication/ui/component/WalkthroughHorizontalImageCarousel.kt
IDEA additional info:
Subsystem: com.intellij.openapi.diff.impl.patch.CharsetEP
<+>UTF-8
===================================================================
diff --git a/onboardingandauthentication/src/main/java/com/ibm/google/onboardingandauthentication/ui/component/WalkthroughHorizontalImageCarousel.kt b/onboardingandauthentication/src/main/java/com/ibm/google/onboardingandauthentication/ui/component/WalkthroughHorizontalImageCarousel.kt
--- a/onboardingandauthentication/src/main/java/com/ibm/google/onboardingandauthentication/ui/component/WalkthroughHorizontalImageCarousel.kt	(revision a2f4d0f0024a9e7b91a51bbb1fe89f75cdaa1812)
+++ b/onboardingandauthentication/src/main/java/com/ibm/google/onboardingandauthentication/ui/component/WalkthroughHorizontalImageCarousel.kt	(date 1755841699455)
@@ -81,16 +81,16 @@
     override val values: Sequence<List<WalkthroughStepModel>> = sequenceOf(
         listOf(
             WalkthroughStepModel(
-                imageId = R.drawable.ic_walkthrough_music,
-                description = "Listen to relaxing music"
+                imageId = R.drawable.ic_walkthrough_sun,
+                description = "Go outside and get some sunshine"
             ),
             WalkthroughStepModel(
                 imageId = R.drawable.ic_walkthrough_blooming,
                 description = "Take a moment to breathe and unwind"
